>\n<p>I'm using nvim as a code editor, mainly for latex and markdown.</p>\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<h3>late...</h3>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-05-17T13:29:39+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["arch", "config", "editor"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/obsidian/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/obsidian/", "title": "obsidian", "content_html": "<h1>obsidian</h1>\n<h2>plugins</h2>\n<p>\u5e38\u7528\uff1a</p>\n<ul>\n<li>remotely save (using webdav to synchronize files)</li>\n<li>obsidian web clipper \u6d4f\u89c8\u5668\u63d2\u4ef6</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\u597d\u7528\uff1a</p>\n<ul>\n<li>find orphaned files and broken links</li>\n<li>...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-05-17T13:29:39+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["config", "editor", "obsidian"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/ssh/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/ssh/", "title": "About ssh", "content_html": "<h1>ssh</h1>\n<h2>\u5185\u7f51ssh\u8fde\u63a5</h2>\n<p>\u4e00\u4e2aipv6\u5730\u5740\u7684\u7535\u8111\uff0c\u4f5c\u4e3a\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\uff0c\u4e00\u4e2a\u5185\u7f51\u7684\u7535\u8111\uff0c\u8bb0\u4f5c\u670d\u52a1\u673a\uff0c\u671f\u671b\u5176\u4ed6\u7684\u5ba2\u6237\u673a\uff08\u6bd4\u5982iphone\uff09\u8fde\u63a5\u5230\u5185\u7f51\u7684\u670d\u52a1\u673a\u3002</p>\n<h3>\u601d\u8def</h3>\n<p>\u5c06\u670d\u52a1\u673a\u7684ssh\u7aef\u53e3\u8f6c\u53d1\u5230\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u7684\u7aef\u53e3\uff0c\u5373\u6570\u636e\u4ece\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u7684\u7aef\u53e3\u4f20\u9001\u5230\u670d\u52a1\u673a\uff1b\u5ba2\u6237\u673a\u8fde\u63a5\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u7684\u7aef\u53e3\u5373\u53ef\u3002\u4e2d\u95f4\u673a\u6709ipv6\u5730\u5740\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5ssh...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-05-17T13:29:39+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["tools"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/sync/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/sync/", "title": "\u5404\u79cd\u540c\u6b65\u65b9\u6cd5", "content_html": "<h1>\u5404\u79cd\u4e91\u540c\u6b65\u65b9\u6cd5</h1>\n<h2>\u4e91\u76d8</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>koofr</li>\n<li>onedrive</li>\n<li>ali</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\u6587\u4ef6\u540c\u6b65\u65b9\u6cd5</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>webdav \u534f\u8bae</li>\n<li>rclone \u547d\u4ee4\u884c\u5de5\u5177</li>\n</ul>\n<p>rclone --filter-from list.txt localdir remote:target</p>\n<p>without</p>\n<p>```txt\n- **...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-05-17T13:29:39+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["tools"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/vimtex/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/vimtex/", "title": "Write latex with neovim", "content_html": "<h1>Write latex with neovim</h1>\n<p>$\\latex$</p>\n<h2>vimtex</h2>\n<p><code>vimtex</code>\u57fa\u672c\u4e0a\u662f\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u5168\u5957\u7684\u529f\u80fd\uff0c\u5305\u62ec</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u76ee\u5f55\uff0c\u6807\u7b7e\u7b49</li>\n<li>\u5404\u79cd\u73af\u5883\uff0c<code>insert</code>\u6a21\u5f0f\u4e0b\u7684\u5404\u79cdsnippets\uff0c<code>normal</code>\u6a21\u5f0f\u4e0b\u7684\u6587\u672c\u5bf9\u8c61\u548c\u547d\u4ee4</li>\n<li>\u7f16\u8bd1\uff0c\u62a5\u9519</li>\n<li>\u6b63\u5411\u641c\u7d22\uff08\u4ecetex\u5b9a\u4f4d\u5230pdf...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-05-17T13:29:39+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["config", "editor", "latex"]}, {"id": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/virtual-machine/", "url": "https://hiraethecho.github.io/wiki/code/virtual-machine/", "title": "qemu\u865a\u62df\u673a", "content_html": "<h1>qemu\u865a\u62df\u673a</h1>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<p>Install pakages</p>\n<p>```arch\nparu -S qemu-base # basic\nparu -S libvirt # \u865a\u62df\u673a\u4e00\u4e9bapi\u7684\u5c01\u88c5\nvirtual-manager # GUI\nparu -S dnsmasq bridge-utils # ...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2025-05-17T13:29:39+00:00", "authors": [], "tags": ["tools"]}]}